[137.374356, "o", "# TD-001: Temperature Conversion\r\n\r\n## References\r\n\r\n- PRD: `docs/helix/01-frame/prd.md` — Features F1, F2, F3\r\n- User Story: `docs/helix/01-frame/user-stories/US-001-temperature-conversion.md`\r\n\r\n## Overview\r\n\r\nA single-file Node.js module (`bin/convert.js`) that converts temperatures between Fahrenheit and Celsius. It serves as both the CLI entry point and the importable module.\r\n\r\n## Module: `bin/convert.js`\r\n\r\n### Exported Functions\r\n\r\n```js\r\n"]
[137.37438, "o", "function toFahrenheit(c) — returns (c * 9/5) + 32\r\nfunction toCelsius(f)    — returns (f - 32) * 5/9\r\n```\r\n\r\n"]
[137.374553, "o", "...\r\n\r\n"]
