[141.377228, "o", "$ claude -p \"Read the user story at docs/helix/01-frame/user-stories/US-001-temperature-conversion.md and the technical design at docs/helix/02-design/technical-designs/TD-001-temperature-conversion.md. You MUST create ALL of the following files: (1) docs/helix/03-test/test-plans/TP-001-temperature-conversion.md, (2) package.json with contents: {\"name\":\"hello-helix\",\"version\":\"0.1.0\",\"scripts\":{\"test\":\"node --test\"}}, (3) tests/convert.test.js using node:test and node:assert that requires ../bin/convert.js for toFahrenheit and toCelsius functions, tests toFahrenheit(0) === 32.0, toCelsius(212) === 100.0, and toCelsius(98.6) is approximately 37.0. Do NOT create bin/convert.js — the tests MUST fail.\"\r\n\r\n"]
